# ðŸ›  Pro Tip
âœ… Combine these paths with tools like:
- `ffuf -w wordlist.txt -u https://target/FUZZ/`
- `dirsearch -u https://target.com -w wordlist.txt`
- `gobuster dir -u https://target.com -w wordlist.txt -x php,html,js,json`
  
âœ… Always try:
- `-x` extension brute-forcing (`php,html,json`)
- **Lowercase** and **Uppercase** versions (`admin`, `Admin`, `ADMIN`)

